text.tspan: Ribosome - turns RNA + amino acids into proteins
Smooth ER - lipids, other metabolic processes
Golgi apparatus - makes lysosomes, transports things to other places
Lysosomes - break down big things in the cell
Nucleoid - like nucleus but less so
Peroxiome - get rid of toxins, uses up oxygen
Signal - Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Bluegreen
